<h3 id="手动挂载">手动挂载</h3>
<p>将准备好的目录挂在到 merged:</p>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>mount overlay -t overlay -o <span style="color:#f5e0dc">lowerdir</span><span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span>/root/rootfs-init:/root/rootfs,upperdir<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span>/root/diff,workdir<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span>/root/work /root/merged</span></span></code></pre></div>
<h3 id="使用容器">使用容器</h3>
<p>利用 chroot 改变根文件系统</p>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#89dceb">cd</span> merged
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> apk update
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> apk upgrade
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> apk add gcc
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> gcc -v
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> apk add neofetch
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>chroot <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$PWD</span> neofetch</span></span></code></pre></div>
